### 1ï¸âƒ£ flake8ï¼ˆåŸºæœ¬ãƒã‚§ãƒƒã‚¯ï¼‰

```bash
# å®Ÿè¡Œ
flake8 sample.py

# å‡ºåŠ›ä¾‹
sample.py:1:1: F401 'sys' imported but unused
sample.py:2:1: F401 'os' imported but unused
sample.py:6:11: E225 missing whitespace around operator
sample.py:8:15: E225 missing whitespace around operator
```

**è¨­å®šãƒ•ã‚¡ã‚¤ãƒ«ä½œæˆ**

```ini
# .flake8 ã¾ãŸã¯ setup.cfg
