```

### Makefileã§è‡ªå‹•åŒ–

```makefile
# Makefile
.PHONY: format lint test

format:
	black .
	isort .

lint:
	flake8 .
	pylint src/
	mypy src/

test:
	pytest tests/ -v --cov=src

all: format lint test
```

