    """Calculate sum of two numbers."""
    result: int = x + y
    return result
```

**åŠ¹æœ / Benefits:**
- âœ… èª°ãŒæ›¸ã„ã¦ã‚‚åŒã˜ã‚¹ã‚¿ã‚¤ãƒ« / Same style regardless of author
